      • JetHeaderBuilder

        public JetHeaderBuilder(String authHeaderValue)
        Create a new HeaderBuilder instance
        Parameters:
        authHeaderValue - The authorization header value from the jet configuration. This is the value of JetConfig.getAuthorizationHeaderValue(). If not empty, then this will add a header "Authentication" with the specified value.
